## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources, which may not cover all aspects of the complex relationship between society and science. Some sources may lack peer-reviewed credibility, and the perspectives presented might not encompass all cultural or historical contexts. Additionally, the dynamic nature of this relationship means that new developments could alter current understandings. Further research, including empirical studies and expert interviews, would provide a more comprehensive view.